---
// ExtractionProcessSection.astro — 5-step botanical extraction timeline
---

<section class="extraction-section bg-noise" id="extraction-process" aria-label="Extraction Process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="extraction-inner">
      <!-- Left: header + timeline -->
      <div class="extraction-content">
        <div class="section-header" style="text-align:left; margin:0 0 3rem;">
          <span class="section-label">How We Work</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Precision Extraction <em>Process</em></h2>
          <p class="section-desc">
            From raw botanical material to pharmaceutical-grade active compounds — every step is validated, documented, and traceable.
          </p>
        </div>

    <div class="process-timeline" role="list">

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="process-step" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-connector">
          <div class="step-node">
            <span class="step-num">01</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content glass reveal">
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌿</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Raw Material Sourcing</h3>
            <p>We partner with certified botanical farms and wild-harvest cooperatives to secure authentic, pesticide-free plant materials — roots, leaves, bark, and seeds — fully traceable to their origin regions.</p>
            <ul class="step-tags">
              <li>GAP Certified Farms</li>
              <li>Species Authentication</li>
              <li>Heavy Metal Pre-screen</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="process-step" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-connector">
          <div class="step-node">
            <span class="step-num">02</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content glass reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Advanced Extraction</h3>
            <p>Our partner GMP plant employs supercritical CO₂ extraction, water-ethanol solvent systems, and membrane separation technologies to maximize yield of target active molecules while preserving purity.</p>
            <ul class="step-tags">
              <li>sCO₂ Extraction</li>
              <li>Solvent Residue Control</li>
              <li>Continuous Process Monitoring</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="process-step" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-connector">
          <div class="step-node">
            <span class="step-num">03</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content glass reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔬</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Chromatographic Purification</h3>
            <p>Crude extracts undergo column chromatography (preparative HPLC or resin column) isolation to achieve monomer purity ≥98%, removing plant matrix compounds and concentrating the active constituent.</p>
            <ul class="step-tags">
              <li>Preparative HPLC</li>
              <li>Resin Column Separation</li>
              <li>Purity ≥98%</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 4 -->
      <div class="process-step" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-connector">
          <div class="step-node">
            <span class="step-num">04</span>
          </div>
          <div class="step-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content glass reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true">🛡️</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Quality & Analytical Testing</h3>
            <p>Every batch is tested by HPLC (purity), ICP-MS (heavy metals), GC-MS (pesticide & solvents), and microbial plate count before release. Third-party SGS or Eurofins reports available on request.</p>
            <ul class="step-tags">
              <li>HPLC Purity Testing</li>
              <li>ICP-MS Heavy Metals</li>
              <li>USP/EP Method Compliance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 5 -->
      <div class="process-step process-step--last" role="listitem">
        <div class="step-connector">
          <div class="step-node step-node--final">
            <span class="step-num">05</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-content glass reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="step-icon" aria-hidden="true">📦</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <h3>Packaging & Global Dispatch</h3>
            <p>Finished ingredients are packaged under inert nitrogen atmosphere in food-grade sealed bags (1kg, 5kg, 25kg drums), with COA, MSDS, and specification sheets included for every shipment.</p>
            <ul class="step-tags">
              <li>Nitrogen-flush Packaging</li>
              <li>COA Included</li>
              <li>DDP / ExW / FOB Available</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Bottom CTA -->
    <div class="process-cta">
      <a href="/quality" class="btn btn--outline">View Full Quality Standards</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--gold">Request a Sample</a>
    </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Right: sticky image stack -->
      <div class="extraction-visual" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="vis-img vis-img--top">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1582719508461-905c673771fd?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=70"
            alt="Industrial botanical extraction reactor vessels"
            loading="lazy" width="600" height="400"
          />
          <div class="vis-overlay"></div>
          <div class="vis-label">GMP Extraction Plant</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vis-img vis-img--bottom">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757175-5700dde675bc?w=500&auto=format&fit=crop&q=70"
            alt="HPLC analytical instruments in quality control lab"
            loading="lazy" width="600" height="300"
          />
          <div class="vis-overlay"></div>
          <div class="vis-label">QC Laboratory</div>
        </div>
        <div class="vis-stat-card">
          <div class="vis-stat">
            <span class="vis-stat-num">500+</span>
            <span class="vis-stat-label">Products Tested Monthly</span>
          </div>
          <div class="vis-stat">
            <span class="vis-stat-num">≥98%</span>
            <span class="vis-stat-label">Standard Purity Target</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .extraction-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-4xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .extraction-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 10%;
    left: -5%;
    width: 40%;
    height: 80%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(212, 166, 84, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── Two-column inner layout ── */
  .extraction-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .extraction-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* ── Visual panel ── */
  .extraction-visual {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .vis-img {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .vis-img img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .vis-img--top img { aspect-ratio: 3/2; }
  .vis-img--bottom img { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }

  .vis-img:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }

  .vis-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(6,5,3,0.6) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .vis-label {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0.75rem;
    left: 0.875rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .vis-stat-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .vis-stat {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .vis-stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .vis-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .extraction-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }
    .extraction-visual { position: static; }
  }

  /* ── Timeline ── */
  .process-timeline {
    margin-top: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .process-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .process-step--last .step-line {
    display: none;
  }

  /* ── Step connector ── */
  .step-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .step-node {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-bg-deep);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(212, 166, 84, 0.2);
    transition: box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .process-step:hover .step-node {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow-gold);
  }

  .step-node--final {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent));
    border-color: var(--color-primary-light);
  }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .step-node--final .step-num {
    color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .step-line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--color-primary), transparent);
    opacity: 0.3;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ── Step Content ── */
  .step-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border-color: rgba(212, 166, 84, 0.1) !important;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .step-content:hover {
    border-color: rgba(212, 166, 84, 0.25) !important;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow-gold);
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .step-body h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .step-body p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-tags li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .process-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .process-step {
      grid-template-columns: 40px 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .step-node {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
    }

    .step-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
